<item>
            <title>[KAFKA-12332] Error partitions from topics with invalid IDs in LISR requests</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-12332</link>
                <project id="12311720" key="KAFKA">Kafka</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In a situation where topics are deleted and recreated in a short amount of time, LeaderAndIsr requests can contain topics with invalid IDs, but correct epochs. In this case, we will incorrectly handle the request and simply log an error message on the broker. It will be more useful to not handle the request for the partition with an invalid ID and send and error back to the controller.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
